{"tid":425382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）想同朋友一齊開鋪","createTime":"2017-10-05T16:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T02:08:56.000Z","uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96aceae122df27fb86d1529a79e1f6f4a17c302c","tid":425382,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"我同朋友諗住一齊合資開間甜品鋪，我朋友係法國藍帶，所以佢會負責比較技術層面既野，而我就會負責行政、業務方面。我宜家草擬緊一份合夥既合同。假如我地間鋪有一定客源之後佢突然起我飛腳自己開過令一間，想問我有冇方法可以令到我有保障？"},{"pid":"43e95f39b26f01ef7718867a8b4818d02cdc216d","tid":425382,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef1aed7d7bc4b498142396667fa3d6e79f2e95ba","tid":425382,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"買刀"},{"pid":"61138e1649b086c454ac5ed5b8e5f839760b3f92","tid":425382,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"唯有跟佢學幾招囉睇佢肯唔肯教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係無得點 技術係人地到"},{"pid":"74590c4fe8c6b5ee78a3dbe0223f6d74ebd85625","tid":425382,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:02:38.000Z","msg":"合約bound佢唔離開幾多年內唔比去其他餐廳做<br />\n個profit allocation method公平啲，同佢打好啲關係正常都唔會走啦"},{"pid":"966694454981a039a7117c5aa60acc8259d6d792","tid":425382,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唯有跟佢學幾招囉睇佢肯唔肯教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係無得點 技術係人地到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898071353c17eb42648071f7954cdeb15074f90b","tid":425382,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T01:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>合約bound佢唔離開幾多年內唔比去其他餐廳做<br />\n個profit allocation method公平啲，同佢打好啲關係正常都唔會走啦</blockquote><br />\n份合約都會盡量做到最公平，最驚係